---
import Layout from "../../components/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="About" description="A calm bio, why writing matters, and a short principles list." currentPath="/about">
  <article class="content">
    <h1>About</h1>

    <section style="margin-top: 24px;">
      <h2>A calm bio</h2>
      <p>
        MJ builds small things on purpose. The work lives somewhere between software, play,
        and quiet observation. This site is a long-term notebook: steady, minimal, and
        allowed to change slowly.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section style="margin-top: 32px;">
      <h2>Why I write</h2>
      <p>
        Writing keeps decisions visible. It turns impulse into intent, and it leaves a trail
        that can be revisited later.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section style="margin-top: 32px;">
      <h2>Principles</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Keep things readable.</li>
        <li>Prefer small, finished work over endless expansion.</li>
        <li>Choose calm defaults.</li>
        <li>Ship in slices.</li>
        <li>Respect attention.</li>
      </ul>
    </section>
  </article>
</Layout>
